name: Diluc -  LoRAs collections of Trauter's
description:
https://huggingface.co/YoungMasterFromSect/Trauter_LoRAs collection of Anime LoRAs that include characters from various series.

Every day I try atleast to add 1 LoRA to the collection.

It has guide on what LoRAs are, and how to use them.

I also included images with metadata and sample prompts.

Those are my personal LoRAs made with my usecase in mind. I don't guarantee that they will produce results that you are searching for.
